name: Warp Flyer
description:
In this fast pace game you will fly above a road filled with obstacles and warp through the space to new sections of the universe.

This game is an endless runner where you will move side to side to avoid obstacles in the road while gaining more and more time and raising your score. Be aware that every star gate you go through will send you to a new area in the universe that could make the road a lot more of a danger. With the option to Boost up at any point get ready to test your keyboard as you reach a speed of 800.

With a total of 10 vehicles you can play in multiple ways with the different speed and health of each one.

With 15 challenges in total to test your ability to move, boost, and stay alive.

Warp Flayer
